with cte as(
    select a.date, a.POG, a.subOrderId, b.Channel 
    from (
            select a.POG, b.subOrderId, to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000)) as date 
            from `temp.disablePogs` a left join `last20Days(agCmDump)` b 
            on a.POG=b.pogId 
            where to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000))>='2023-03-19' and to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000))<='2023-03-21'
        ) a 
    left join `temp.orderAttri` b 
    on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
)

select count(distinct subOrderId)/3 as SD_ADS, count(distinct case when lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subOrderId end)/3 as FB_ADS 
from cte 
",1000)
